---
title: Banana Blossom & Paella-Style Baked Rice with Baby Spinach & Roasted Almonds
description: Banana blossom and smoked paprika add another super-tasty dimension to this delicious paella-style baked
rice. Serve it with roasted almonds for a delightful crunch that pairs so well with 'al dente' baked rice!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
